headline: 2 Reasons to Like AMGN and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Although Amgen (currently trading at $299.86 per share) has gained 9.6% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 29.3% return during that period. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
